'''NGC 1360'''，或稱為'''知更鳥蛋星雲'''（Robin's Egg Nebula）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.myastrostuff.com/pncollection/ngc1360.htm |title=NGC 1360 Robin's Egg |access-date=2016-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224735/http://www.myastrostuff.com/pncollection/ngc1360.htm |archive-date=2016-03-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，是一個位於天爐座的[[行星狀星雲|行星狀星雲]]。該星雲因為光譜中強烈的[[氧|OIII]]譜線而被歸類為行星狀星雲。一般相信該星雲的前身星在最後崩潰成為行星狀星雲以前，它在可見光影像中偏紅色的物質已經完全被拋出<ref name=astro>{{Cite web |url=http://www.astrosurf.com/antilhue/ngc1360.htm |title=Astrosurf NGC 1360 in FORNAX |accessdate=2016-12-06 |archive-date=2017-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415020401/http://www.astrosurf.com/antilhue/ngc1360.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它的表面光度略低於[[IC_2003|IC 2003]]。

NGC 1360由德國天文學家{{link-en|弗里德里希·奧古斯特·特奧多爾·溫尼克|Friedrich August Theodor Winnecke}}發現<ref>{{cite web
 | url = http://messier.seds.org/xtra/Bios/winnecke.html
 | title = Friedrich August Theodor Winnecke (February 5, 1835 - December 3, 1897)
 | author = Students for the Exploration and Development of Space
 | date = 
 | work = 
 | publisher = http://seds.org/
 | accessdate = March 18, 2012
 | archive-date = 2017-06-04
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170604124424/http://messier.seds.org/xtra/Bios/winnecke.html
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。

